Package: stomachr
Title: Download and Clean ICES Stomach Content Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Max", "Lindmark", email = "max.lindmark@slu.se",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tidy pipeline for downloading and cleaning ICES stomach content
    data from the four-table relational schema used by the ICES stomach content
    database (stomachdata.ices.dk). Produces a single flat tibble suitable for
    individual-level diet analysis.
